building.name: The Plaza
building.description: The Plaza is a tall building of 38 storeys that is of walking distance to Plaza Indonesia, Grand Indonesia Shopping Town and Sarinah Plaza. The Plaza is equipped with 20 lifts that is split into 3 zones, namely Low Zone, Mid Zone and High Zone, and a dedicated service lift and executive lift.
building.address: Jl. M.H. Thamrin No. 28-30 Jakarta Pusat, Jakarta, Indonesia
